        <p><b>POSITION:</b> SENIOR MANAGER (FINANCIAL SERVICES)<br><br>

<b>LOCATION:</b> OWERRI<br><br>

<b>REPORTING LINE:</b> GROUP HEAD, FINANCIAL SERVICES<br>

ABC Transport Plc is a leading, integrated transport and logistics company in

Nigeria and West Africa. We require the services of a Senior Manager

(Financial Services).<br><br>

<b>MINIMUM QUALIFICATION AND EXPERIENCE REQUIRED</b><br>

. BSC/HND in Accounting from a reputable institution plus ACA<br>

. Minimum of 10 years post NYSC experience of which at least 7 years

must be post ACA<br>

. Must be very conversant with IFRS reporting<br>

. Demonstrate a good understanding of financial reporting under group

settings<br>

. Knowledgeable in Taxation and Treasury Management<br>

. Good understanding of ERP systems<br>

. Ability to work under pressure and lead a large team<br>

. Between the ages of 35 and 45 years<br><br>

<b>KEY RESPONSIBILTIES:</b><br>

. Coordination of the financial reporting system to produce IFRS

compliant group financial statements on timely basis.<br>

. Managing the financial control system, cost and management accounting

and taxation<br>

. Deputizing for the Chief Financial Officer as may be required from time

to time<br><br>

<b>METHOD OF APPLICATION</b><br>

Interested and qualified applicants should submit their application with

comprehensive resume to: <b>hr_resume2015@yahoo.com</b> <strong>or</strong><br>

<b>The PEOPLE MANAGER<br>

ABC Transport Plc<br>

KM 5, MCC/Uratta Road<br>

Owerri.</b><br><br>



Applications should be submitted not later than <b>April 23, 2017</b>.</p>
